sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as K8s API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant BFF as BFF Sidecar (e.g. gen-ai)<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(OGX, MLflow, MaaS, etc.)

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 1: Dashboard UI Load
    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>X-Forwarded headers
    KRBAC->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>(projects:list)
    K8sAPI-->>KRBAC: Authenticated + Authorized
    KRBAC->>Backend: GET / (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups
    Backend-->>KRBAC: React SPA (static assets)
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 2: K8s API Proxy (Pass-Through)
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User
    Backend->>K8sAPI: K8s API Call (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s Resource Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: JSON Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: K8s Resource Data

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: Module Federation BFF Proxy (Sidecar Mode)
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/ogx/... (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User
    Backend->>BFF: Proxy /_mf/gen-ai/* (HTTPS/8143)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>Upstream: API Call (HTTPS)<br/>Auth: user_token
    Upstream-->>BFF: API Response
    BFF-->>Backend: Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Module API Data

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 4: WebSocket K8s Watch
    Browser->>Gateway: WS Upgrade /wss/k8s/* (WSS/443)<br/>Bearer token in subprotocol
    Gateway->>KRBAC: WS Upgrade (WSS/8443)<br/>Subprotocol token
    KRBAC->>Backend: WS Upgrade (WS/8080)<br/>Decoded Bearer token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WS Watch (WSS/6443)<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch Events (stream)
    Backend-->>KRBAC: Events (stream)
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Events (stream)
    Gateway-->>Browser: K8s Watch Events

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 5: Inter-BFF Communication (Gen-AI → MaaS)
    Browser->>Gateway: POST /_mf/gen-ai/api/v1/maas/... (HTTPS/443)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>BFF: Proxy to gen-ai BFF (HTTPS/8143)
    participant MaaS as MaaS BFF<br/>8243/TCP HTTPS
    BFF->>MaaS: Inter-BFF call (HTTPS/8243)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    participant MaaSCtrl as MaaS Controller<br/>HTTPS
    MaaS->>MaaSCtrl: API Call (HTTPS)<br/>user_token
    MaaSCtrl-->>MaaS: MaaS Response
    MaaS-->>BFF: Response
    BFF-->>Backend: Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: MaaS Data
